Package net.sf.debianmaven

Class PackageMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • net.sf.debianmaven.AbstractDebianMojo
        • net.sf.debianmaven.PackageMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo
    public class PackageMojo
extends AbstractDebianMojo
    Generates a Debian package. Uses Debian utilities: dpkg-deb and fakeroot.
    Goal name of this mojo:
    package
    Default phase:
    package
    This goal requires dependencies to be resolved.
